pageContext.claim: “I had a leader of a country call up, he's a very tough leader, tough as hell, they're gonna figure it out maybe, although they wouldn't if it was right, if it was good they were not gonna report it. And he said, 'I hope Biden doesn't win because he's always sleeping.' This is a killer. Says, 'I hope he doesn't win 'cause he's always sleeping.' You know, I thought he was being funny.”
pageContext.analysis: This obviously cannot be confirmed but it seems to be a made-up story. A foreign leader is really going to call Trump and describe Biden with a turn of the same phrase -- sleepy -- that Trump uses?
